<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 10:53PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...Black Ice Possible on Area Roads...
The combination of wet snow and drizzle earlier this evening and
temperatures now dropping below freezing will result in some slick
spots on area roads. Drivers should use caution this evening and
be alert to potential icy spots on the roads, especially on
bridges and overpasses.</description>
